  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 10 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel will be provided from the 10th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Electricity and Energy Minister Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera said today (3) afternoon that he hopes that the people will be able to get fuel without interruption from the 10th of this month and once again apologize for the economic damage and inconvenience caused to the people.",
        "The minister said that the ordered fuel stock will reach Sri Lanka from the 8th and also mentioned that if the fuel is continuously received after that, it will be enough for one month."
      ],
